@realmoney With the after hours announcement that Trump is retaliating further against China we now likely have certainty. For those that anticipated (and shorted the market) in the belief that this cold/trade war would intensify we were paid off today. First level thinking is

How do talking heads have answers to every question regardless of their backgrounds, body of knowledge and general expertise? I have never understood when option specialists and floor traders talk about strategy and economics. Or when strategists talk about individual

companies. Or when technicians talks about fundamentals. Or when fundamentalists talk about charts. Or bitcoin mavens talk about everything. Or professors talk about markets. Maybe its me but fin media tries to make authoritative generalists out of specialists.
Too often the fin media are victims of "group stink" and try to make stars out of us common folk. There are some things to think about over the weekend and for the remainder of the year.
